{"tid":2108962,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥迪奧拿公開反擊：摩佬高普唔該收嗲！這是足球美好的一天，非常美好的一天！","createTime":"2020-07-15T02:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T03:20:36.000Z","uid":103207,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"535c815908ccd29ec5abd75e4a7a06e7004f12a8","tid":2108962,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:07:04.000Z","msg":"哥迪奧拿公開反擊：摩帥高普該收聲！<br />\n<br />\n  摩連奴（Jose Mourinho）和高普（Jurgen Klopp）對曼城解禁發表看法，<span class=\"red\">哥迪奧拿（Pep Guardiola）感到不快，他回應說：這些議論的人該閉嘴並且道歉。</span><br />\n<br />\n  「<span class=\"red\">我告訴祖斯（摩連奴）和祖爾根（高普），這是足球美好的一天，非常美好的一天</span>，」哥迪奧拿說，「<span class=\"red\">我們和其他人一樣遵守規則，如果破壞規則，那麼我們該被禁</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n  「人們背後議論我們有多少次了？我希望他們結束，看著我們的眼睛，面對面和我們說。如果我們在球場上輸了，握手認輸，但他們必須到球場上來試圖擊敗我們，紳士一點，就像我們一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n  「<span class=\"red\">祖斯和其他主教練應該清楚，我們的聲譽遭到了損害，我們應該聽到他們的道歉</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/07/13/a/ae57512fa0c4c1827d4b5e76a3bef35a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F07%2F13%2Fa%2Fae57512fa0c4c1827d4b5e76a3bef35a.jpg&h=3ba72219&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f41d5a5f141e8eeffe96ef7885055a48e3f6e9a","tid":2108962,"uid":5026,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:09:12.000Z","msg":"咁似黑警講嘢嘅"},{"pid":"157b28a250eaf6435e747ed304bdf6af90bebe28","tid":2108962,"uid":28435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"哥狗：法治未死，任何人想踐踏佢，OMDB"},{"pid":"a272d771bd100bd5c40b3b1a03ca8a4d654350ea","tid":2108962,"uid":357421,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:10:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93ca82f97ebac11d0546d76f8d6bdd753a9d1b24","tid":2108962,"uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"157b28a250eaf6435e747ed304bdf6af90bebe28","tid":2108962,"uid":28435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"哥狗：法治未死，任何人想踐踏佢，OMDB"